org.cloudgraph.hbase.io

Class GraphRowReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.state.GraphRow
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.io.GraphRowReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RowOperation, RowReader, RowState, State

    public class GraphRowReader
extends GraphRow
implements RowReader
    The operational, configuration and other state information required for read operations on a single graph row.

    Acts as a single component within a TableReader container and encapsulates the HBase client Get operation for use in read operations across multiple logical entities within a graph row.

    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
